OL,3,C'Be careful' - Pensioner warns against
OL,4,C'horrible' Amazon giftcard scam
OL,6,FA pensioner who was almost conned out
OL,7,Fof thousands of pounds via an online
OL,8,Fscam is issuing a warning to others
OL,9,Ffollowing what he says was a horrible
OL,10,Fexperience.
OL,12,FChris Hope from Stubbington, Hampshire
OL,13,Fwas called by a hoaxer he thought was
OL,14,Ffrom Amazon and ended up inadvertently
OL,15,Fpaying for internet gift cards.
OL,17,FThe 86-year-old had a call from a
OL,18,Fwoman claiming to be from Amazon, he
OL,19,Fsays he was sceptical, until she
OL,20,Falerted him to the fact a man's name
OL,21,Fhad been added to his Amazon account.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
