OL,3,C'Be careful' - Pensioner warns against
OL,4,C'horrible' Amazon giftcard scam
OL,6,FMr Hope was then told to enter a
OL,7,Fseries of codes into his phone, which
OL,8,Fhe now thinks activated the purchase
OL,9,Fof more than #2,000 worth of assorted
OL,10,Fgift cards.
OL,12,FChristopher Hope said: ''It was the
OL,13,Ffact that they didn't give me a link.
OL,14,FThey asked me to go into my account,
OL,15,Fand there was the gentleman there.
OL,17,F"Then when I went into my basket,
OL,18,Fthere were 17 items, a list of gift
OL,19,Fcards that they bought. So I thought,
OL,20,Fit's them.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
