OL,3,C'Be careful' - Pensioner warns against
OL,4,C'horrible' Amazon giftcard scam
OL,6,F"Just be very careful. I thought I was
OL,7,Ffairly switched on with this but I
OL,8,Ffell for it hook line and sinker.
OL,10,F"It was horrible, I'm really upset
OL,11,Fbecause it could happen to lots of
OL,12,Fother people who maybe wouldn't
OL,13,Frealise."
OL,15,FThis scam works by fraudsters
OL,16,Freceiving the cards electronically and
OL,17,Fcashing them in before the ruse is
OL,18,Fdetected.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
