OL,4,C'horrible' Amazon giftcard scam
OL,6,FMr Hope was alerted by a real Amazon
OL,7,Fworker to the fact someone in another
OL,8,Fcountry had accessed his account, and
OL,9,Fhe then shut it down.
OL,11,FIn the end, the gift card company
OL,12,Fcancelled most of Mr Hope's
OL,13,Ftransactions, suspecting fraud, and
OL,14,Freimbursed him for #400 worth of
OL,15,Fpayments that did go through.
OL,17,FGiftcard scams are just one of many
OL,18,Ffloating around the internet and
OL,19,Fcosting the UK more than a billion
OL,20,Fpounds every year.
