OL,3,C'Be careful' - Pensioner warns against
OL,4,C'horrible' Amazon giftcard scam
OL,6,FRob Lilley-Jones, Consumer Expert for
OL,7,FWhich said: "Unfortunately, these
OL,8,Ftypes of scams are increasingly common.
OL,10,F"What we're seeing now is a lot of
OL,11,Ftechnology used by scammers, they're
OL,12,Foften using artificial intelligence to
OL,13,Fin effect clone the voice of a family,
OL,14,Ffriend or indeed one of these well
OL,15,Fknown companies which can mean they
OL,16,Fseem increasingly legitimate.
OL,18,F"They are very common and when it
OL,19,Fcomes to giftcard scam it can be a
OL,20,Freal issue because it can often be
OL,21,Fvery hard to get your money back."
