OL,6,FThe company says it works to remove
OL,7,Ftens of thousands of fake websites and
OL,8,Fscam phone numbers every year.
OL,10,FAn Amazon spokesperson said: "Scammers
OL,11,Fthat attempt to impersonate Amazon put
OL,12,Fconsumers at risk.
OL,14,F"We will continue to invest in
OL,15,Fprotecting consumers and educating the
OL,16,Fpublic on scam avoidance.
